                  <h2>Bringing Long-Distance Collaboration to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Next Level, or Why Itransition Opened an Office in the UK</h2>
                  <div class="read-time">Reading time: 15 min.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="intro-bottom">
                <div class="intro-bottom_left">
