                                                  </th>
                                                  <td data-title="USA">Information is given from the business needs are describedthe way the owner sees them. The vision is board.</td>
                                                  <td data-title="UK">Requirements are more technical and issue oriented. The goal is to solve a particular issue here and now: automate a process, engineer code, develop a module. The vision is more narrow.</td>
